Here's what Cait & I will be bringing tonight.
Kevin


Bavarian Dunkelweiss
--------------------

5 lb wheat malt
4 lb German Munich (10L)
1 lb Carapils
8 oz Caravienne
3 oz Special-B
2 oz Chocolate malt

(mashed wheat malt at 104F for 30 mins then 132F for 30 mins,
added remainder of malts and mashed at 152F for 70 mins,
sparged to collect 6.5 gallons)

0.5 oz Hallertauer (4%AA) at 60 min, 30 min and aroma

Wyeast Weihenstephan 1 quart starter

SG 1.050
FG 1.008
